  <brief_title>Evaluation of Preoperative Use of Pregabalin on Postoperative Analgesia After Laparoscopic Colorectal Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Preemptive Use of Pregabalin on Pain Intensity and Postoperative Morphine Consumption After Laparoscopic Colorectal Surgery</official_title>
